data.description: This property exudes extravagance in every way and has every bell and whistle you could think off ! 4 full bedrooms with 4 full bathrooms, porcelain tile, front/rear garage doors along with a rear private gate, a master bedroom/bathroom that is completely eye watering and two balconies ! It certainly feels like that whatever you can think of you need in a home, this one has got it.  Easy to show and ready to go ! it is a must see in this price range.
